{"tid":1266243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登要為香港人既精神健康岀一分力","createTime":"2019-06-29T13:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:25:18.000Z","uid":106870,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1b53501da06ec24c8ffb5368b160c2b1405fd36e","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"我相信冇一個香港人會想再有任何同伴因為港共政權而陪上性命，無論係岀於任何目的，為咗乜嘢理想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家由6.9 6.12一路走到今日，有人可以一路堅持，但亦有唔少人會覺得心灰意冷、筋疲力盡，好似無論做咩都唔會撼動到呢個政權。<br />\n<br />\n各位仍在為香港岀力既巴絲，請唔好對呢班人惡言相向，真係唔係每一個同路人都有辦法承受到呢種無力感。請大家體諒一下，俾佢哋休息一下。呢場係持久戰，唔可能要所有人長期繃緊精神對抗政權。我哋應該轉換思維，開始準備以月為單位既大型社會不合作運動，務求要全方面、持續咁對政權施壓。<br />\n<br />\n所以，首先要做既就係確保我哋既同路人<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能再少！</span></span>希望大家可以關注下身邊長期為運動付出既戰友，因為你既一個慰問，隨時有可能挽救到一個傍惶無助既靈魂。都請文宣巴絲幫幫手，希望可以岀到啲對抗到失敗主義、抒緩壓力既design<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，仲有餘力既你，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.1見</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbeff2166352b1cce672292a4b7e130d25eb3e97","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"28416943c591d425fb08733cf82f60f2ca4a430c","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c5ce744f07257a837f66c5582c068e79bfbd6b80","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da06336173bb15fad5ef421f517feda7c3cada0a","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:34:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48feb2bb0e19317db0909be1c799f8a6479395e","tid":1266243,"uid":50856,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"記得細個果陣睇卡通片，就係講幕後有個大魔王，靠吸食人既仇恨為食物，佢專係挑動爭鬥，令人類互相殘殺，當人見到同伴受傷，戰死，仇恨就會擴散激化，當人類既仇恨指數節節上升，最終大魔王就會達到佢統治世界既目標。有冇人記得果套係咩卡通片?"},{"pid":"61f0af16a79a3d7737705e1d3ceb251d2180ddb4","tid":1266243,"uid":40787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:35:33.000Z","msg":"推，唔可以再少一人"},{"pid":"3663dc2039a9bb21a3acd57a82ddb23c0142c403","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:37:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"221597e36bca9f977d6dae7d1406ad6983562922","tid":1266243,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:37:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">七一野餐會 <br />\n人數決定一切</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 唔 理 衝 唔 衝 ， 迫 爆 金 紫 荊 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265048\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265048</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">集合地點</span><br />\n<br />\n七一 630AM 修 球場 野餐團集合地點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1265861\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1265861</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n裝備及戰術POST！</span><br />\n<br />\n[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合七一野餐會 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n記得帶gear啦，迫爆至上，人數決定一切</span>"},{"pid":"f1c62e92f17b2fb658c836f8433907a85690d2b3","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c09c2942f6dd179ffbdb343b0e2f9f3ee7f7691a","tid":1266243,"uid":183102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:43:02.000Z","msg":"守望相助，一齊打呢場持久戰！"},{"pid":"dbecc0761467fa1e68274ae161a66ca6af0d6787","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:49:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b09a9269f78415f055211a971c1d5e2bec49eac","tid":1266243,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"40791a2870eaa3e7a645fccbd12fcbf2dae028b8","tid":12662